{"content":"---\ntitle: \"'Loop' cannot have a condition if matching 'Do' has one\"\nms.date: 07/20/2015\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"vbc30238\"\n  - \"bc30238\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"BC30238\"\nms.assetid: 81513cb5-69e7-4d62-b33e-e54cb8c5e8bf\n---\n# 'Loop' cannot have a condition if matching 'Do' has one\nA `Loop` statement contains a `While` or `Until` clause, and the corresponding `Do` statement also contains such a clause. Only one of the `Do` and `Loop` statements in a loop can specify a condition.  \n  \n **Error ID:** BC30238  \n  \n## To correct this error  \n  \n-   Remove the `While` or `Until` clause from either the `Do` statement or the `Loop` statement.  \n  \n## See also\n\n- [Do...Loop Statement](../../visual-basic/language-reference/statements/do-loop-statement.md)\n","nodes":[{"pos":[4,216],"embed":true,"restype":"x-metadata","content":"title: \"'Loop' cannot have a condition if matching 'Do' has one\"\nms.date: 07/20/2015\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"vbc30238\"\n  - \"bc30238\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"BC30238\"\nms.assetid: 81513cb5-69e7-4d62-b33e-e54cb8c5e8bf","nodes":[{"content":"'Loop' cannot have a condition if matching 'Do' has one","nodes":[{"pos":[0,55],"content":"'Loop' cannot have a condition if matching 'Do' has one","nodes":[{"content":"'Loop' cannot have a condition if matching 'Do' has one","pos":[0,55]}]}],"path":["title"],"nosxs":false}],"yml":true},{"pos":[223,278],"content":"'Loop' cannot have a condition if matching 'Do' has one","linkify":"'Loop' cannot have a condition if matching 'Do' has one","nodes":[{"content":"'Loop' cannot have a condition if matching 'Do' has one","pos":[0,55]}]},{"content":"A <ph id=\"ph1\">`Loop`</ph> statement contains a <ph id=\"ph2\">`While`</ph> or <ph id=\"ph3\">`Until`</ph> clause, and the corresponding <ph id=\"ph4\">`Do`</ph> statement also contains such a clause.","pos":[279,401],"source":"A `Loop` statement contains a `While` or `Until` clause, and the corresponding `Do` statement also contai